lines.text:
[as Super Ms. Pac Man, Pepper flies after Super Sue]
Super Suue! I'll get youuu!
[gets chomped by Super Ms. Pac Man and flies off]
What do ya got in the sack, Pac?

[Pinky hides inside a typewriter. Pac-Man comes up, turns the knob on the side to reveal Pinky, then he types the letters "c", "h", "o", "m", and "p"]
What's that say?
[he then chomps Pinky, who flies off]
